channel.title: Missing npcs?
channel.description:
There seems to be npc's missing like romeo in varrock square and some creatures. and you cant talk to people and once i couldnt pick up anything.. But is there any quests you can complete?
And, is there a list of items that have the codes so you can get them using the ::pickup code (like ::pickup 0995 4267504 gives you that amount of money and ::pickup 1282 gives you two steel swords that are noted :P)
It will probably be somewhere (sorry if it already is), its just I'm not very good at this sort of stuff, so help is appreciated.
[[edit. i have found some things, like money that is called null :S, and a dragonstone ring, a rune dagger, and a poisoned black dagger...]]
